head_commit.message:
feat!: remove REST business GET /positions/{code}/assignments (Plan 259-T4)

* feat!: remove REST business GET /api/v1/positions/{code}/assignments (migrate reads to GraphQL); drop route and test; contract SSOT updated; 259A matrix=0

* ci(plan-259A): add post-merge switch workflow to set PLAN259_BUSINESS_GET_THRESHOLD=0 when business GET count is 0 on master

* fix(plan254): unify GraphQL endpoints to monolith (:9090); remove 8090 health checks in E2E config and tests\n\n- CQRS endpoints now map GraphQL to REST monolith (ports.ts)\n- E2E config defaults GRAPHQL_* URLs to :9090 (test-environment.ts)\n- Remove 8090 from TEST_SERVICE_PORTS; rely on monolith health (tests/config/ports.ts)\n\nRationale: Plan 250A runtime unification consolidates GraphQL under the monolith. This fixes Plan 254 gate failures caused by residual 8090 assumptions.

* fix(plan-259-T4): repair OpenAPI paths structure for /api/v1/positions/{code}/assignments post block (remove GET, keep POST under path)

* ci(guard): allow runner compose files at repo root (docker-compose.runner*.yml) in root surface whitelist (Agents Compliance)
